text: Kayle Browning (born July 9, 1992) is an American sport shooter. She participated at the 2018 ISSF World Shooting Championships, winning a medal.Trap team results Browning was an alternate for the 2012 Olympics and has qualified for the 2020 Olympics in trap shooting.
